No. 580. T. N. Barnsdall, Petitioner, v. Thomas S. Waltemeyer. March 5, 1906. Mr. Charles S.- Thomas and Mr. W. H. Bryant for petitioner. Mr. T. Webster Hoyt for respondent.

Petition for a writ of certiorari to the United States Circuit Court of Appeals for the Eighth Circuit denied.
